{"serial": "43045", "department_serial": 41, "code": "IMA005", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Marketing Management In E-Commerce", "ch": "電子商務行銷管理"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chou, En-Yi"], "ch": ["周恩頤"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 6, "session": ["A", "B", "C"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "404"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士在職專班", "en": "Master Programme (Adult Learning)"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 44, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "IMA005是一門了解行銷觀念的基礎課程。本門課程旨在(1)協助學生了解行銷於組織及商業環境中所扮演的角色；(2)讓學生熟習行銷管理之基本概念(例：行銷策略、行銷研究、消費者行為、STP等）；(3)強調學生對於行銷策略與行銷活動之應用；(4)培養學生團隊合作、分析與解決行銷問題的能力。課程內容會融入國、內外之實務案例來闡述行銷觀念的應用，藉以提升同學對行銷議題的興趣。", "en": "IMA005 is an introduction to essentials of marketing concepts. The purpose of this course is to (1) provide students an appreciation and understanding of the role of marketing in an organization as a managerial challenge; (2) familiarize students with the basic concepts of marketing management; (3) enhance the student’s ability in organizing effective marketing strategies and activities; and (4) prepare students to be future managers in different fields with great marketing sense and knowledge."}, "outline": {"ch": "Defining Marketing for the New Realities (Chapter 1)\nMarketing Planning and Management (Chapter 2)\nAnalyzing Consumer Markets (Chapter 3)\nConducting Marketing Research (Chapter 5)\nIdentifying Market Segments (Chapter 6)\nSelecting Target Market(s) (Chapter 6)\nCrafting a Customer Value Proposition and Positioning (Chapter 7)\nDesigning and Managing Products (Chapter 8)\nDesigning and Managing Services (Chapter 9)\nBuilding Strong Brands (Chapter 10)\nManaging Marketing Communication (Chapter 12)\nDesigning an Integrated Marketing Campaign in the Digital Age (Chapter 13)\nBuilding Customer Loyalty (Chapter 19)\nSocially Responsible Marketing (Chapter 21)", "en": "Defining Marketing for the New Realities (Chapter 1)\nMarketing Planning and Management (Chapter 2)\nAnalyzing Consumer Markets (Chapter 3)\nConducting Marketing Research (Chapter 5)\nIdentifying Market Segments (Chapter 6)\nSelecting Target Market(s) (Chapter 6)\nCrafting a Customer Value Proposition and Positioning (Chapter 7)\nDesigning and Managing Products (Chapter 8)\nDesigning and Managing Services (Chapter 9)\nBuilding Strong Brands (Chapter 10)\nManaging Marketing Communication (Chapter 12)\nDesigning an Integrated Marketing Campaign in the Digital Age (Chapter 13)\nBuilding Customer Loyalty (Chapter 19)\nSocially Responsible Marketing (Chapter 21)"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Kotler, P., Keller, K.L., and Chernev, A. (2023)，楊景傅、徐世同譯，行銷管理（第十六版），台北：華泰文化。", "en": "Kotler, P. and Keller, K.L. (2022), Marketing Management Global Edition, 16th Edition, Pearson Education Limited."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "Class Attendance and Participation (Required)\nMidterm Exam (50％)\nFinal Exam (50％)", "en": "Class Attendance and Participation (Required)\nMidterm Exam (50％)\nFinal Exam (50％)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "請來信預約", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理", "en": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}], "en": [{"competenc